John Warner v. Heidi K. Liimatainen Submitted January 5 decided January 26, 1965 Submitted January 11

decided January 26, 1965

Paul B. Groobert, in support of the motion. Henry F. Cooney, in support of the motion. Paul B. Groobert, in opposition.

The motion by the plaintiff to strike an assignment of error in the appeal from the Superior Court in Windham County is denied.

The motion by the defendant to dismiss the plaintiff’s motion to strike an assignment of error in the appeal from the Superior Court in Windham County is denied.
